            Diabetes Training Series
          Heading link



 
Copy link



The ABC’s of Diabetes is a series of three workshops about diabetes, its impact on the body and the importance of keeping it under control, sponsored by the UIC Office of Community Engagement and Neighborhood Health Partnerships.


